    "[player_name]充值了一些账户余额，用这些钱买了电影票。"

# game/r1_movie.rpy:66
translate simplified_chinese r1_movie_e594a3ac:

    # "The movie is starting soon!"
    "电影马上就要开始了！"

# game/r1_movie.rpy:69
